Usage: compare_collections [-help] <collection1> <collection2>
                           [-order_dependent]

-help             # Prints out the command usage
<collection1>     # Specifies the reference collection for comparison
                  # (string, required)
<collection2>     # Specifies the target collection for comparison
                  # (string, required)
-order_dependent  # Order of the objects in both collections must be the same
                  # for the collections to be considered the same (bool, optional)